/*
        exprif.an
    tests ifs inside expressions.

    All if statements return a value,
    although if statements without an
    else return a void value, and if
    statements with an else type-check
    both branches to ensure they match
    in type.
*/

n = if true then 2 else 3

print n

print (if 2 < 1 then 5 else 19)

print (if false then 5 elif true then 1 else 19)
